Step: 00
Copy Server Folder and Paste here 
Then

Npm I express  
Npm I nodemon  

in package.json
  "scripts": {
    "start": "node index.js",
    "dev": "nodemon index.js"
  },

Then Run these Commands
npm i 

In terminal :
	Npm I dotenv   (for .env file )
	Npm I mongoose   (for databse connection)
	Npm I cookie-parser  (for authentication parsing- login/sign)
	Npm I jsonwebtoken
	Npm I nodemailer    (sending mails)
	Npm I otp-generator   (for opt generating)
    Npm I bcrypt (for hashing password)
