Step 00:
Donwload React Start
https://github.com/thepranaygupta/react-tailwind-css-starter-pack
Then move Server Folder in this Folder StudyNotion
Then 

npm i
Then
npm start

Install Concurrently Package to Run both frontend and Backend Simultanolusy

npm i concurrently


Add this two Script in Package.json

    "server": "cd server && npm run dev",
    "dev": "concurrently -n \"client,server\" -c \"bgBlue,bgYellow\" \"npm start\" \"npm run server\""

Like Overall This :
  "scripts": {
    "start": "react-scripts start",
    "build": "react-scripts build",
    "eject": "react-scripts eject",
    "server": "cd server && npm run dev",
    "dev": "concurrently -n \"client,server\" -c \"bgBlue,bgYellow\" \"npm start\" \"npm run server\""
  },